eligibility.additionalValue: To be eligible, you need to be a Tasmanian resident and Australian Citizen.

fees.name: EARLY_REDEMPTION_FEE
fees.additionalInfo: Withdrawal and early redemptions prior to maturity date may be permitted at our discretion. A penalty to the interest rate can be applied and this will vary depending on when during the investment period the redemption occurs.

name: FIXED TERM INVESTMENT
description: More than $5,000 to invest, we have a choice of terms with the certainty of fixed interest rates. At the end of the term you can access the principal and interest earned or choose to reinvest.
